# Crisis Relief Token Distribution System (CRTDS)

A comprehensive blockchain-based platform for transparent emergency aid distribution built on the Stacks blockchain. This smart contract enables humanitarian organizations, government agencies, and NGOs to efficiently distribute aid tokens with full transparency and accountability.

##  Features

- **SIP-010 Compliant**: Full compliance with Stacks fungible token standard
- **Multi-tier Authorization**: Role-based access control with administrators and distributors
- **Recipient Verification**: Comprehensive beneficiary profiling and verification system
- **Batch Processing**: Efficient bulk distribution capabilities
- **Real-time Tracking**: Complete audit trail for all transactions
- **Emergency Response**: Activatable emergency distribution mode
- **Overflow Protection**: Built-in safeguards against mathematical overflow attacks
- **Input Validation**: Comprehensive validation of all user inputs

